{
  "stem": "14897.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I even remember being a little excited about the coming-- possible coming of the war, absolutely not realizing the implications of it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I knew that the, the grownups were very worried.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were brought back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We came back from our vacation a little early.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And everybody was hoarding food, buying a lot of food, and laying in supplies, and all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But when it's-- really, when the bombing started, you know, our first thought was that it was an air raid test, which we had had in the last few days.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But, of course, it turned out to be the real thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As you probably know, Warsaw was besieged for months, so the shock was total and immediate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were bombed day and night because within several days, Warsaw was surrounded.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we were bombed by planes during the day and by artillery at night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The building where we lived was an apartment house because Warsaw is a city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And most of the bombs, by the way, were incendiary type.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And our building was bombed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There were some fires, and we had to escape.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Maybe it was around September 10 or so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I remember that we ran out of the building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The streets were strewn with corpses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as we were running, my mother fell on a body, and I helped her to get up.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I just remember the horror of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We ran to a house of some friends.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we all huddled in a hallway where there were no windows because the windows were broken, and the glass was dangerous.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I remember sitting there-- I'm sure we did other things, but that's my memory, sitting there and praying.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
